# Implementation Plan - Proctored Coding Labs: Competitive & Secure

This plan outlines the steps to upgrade the Coding Labs into a professional, proctored competitive programming environment, featuring automated verification and comprehensive anti-cheating tracking.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Anti-Cheat Restrictions**: We will implement hard blocks on **copying/pasting** and real-time detection of **tab switching**. 
> **Incident Logging**: Every time a student switches tabs or attempts a copy-paste, an "incident" will be logged with a timestamp and sent to the server. Tutors will see a "Proctoring Report" alongside the student's code.

